lzh_formatted:
  title: 題畫扇
  author: 李婷
  language: lzh
  text: 黃葉秋風裏。靑山落照時。江南渺何處。一棹去遲遲。
korean:
  title: 제화선
  author: 이정
  language: kor
  text: |-
    누른 잎은 가을바람 속이요
    푸른 산에 해가 질 때이다
    아득하다 강남의 어느 곳인지
    배 한 척이 느릿느릿 가고 있다
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1450_010_0060&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Inscription on a Painted Fan
  author: Lee Jeong
  language: eng
  text: |-
    Golden leaves drift in the autumn wind,
    Blue mountains bathed in the setting sun.
    Where is that distant Jiangnan,
    where a lone boat drifts slowly on?
  footnotes:
    - Jiangnan refers to the region south of the Yangtze River, a classical symbol of beauty and longing in East Asian poetry.
